  Fix parallel build, configure recursively.

  09 Aug 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> fireflies-2.07.ebuild,
  +files/fireflies-2.07-gcc44.patch:
  Fix building with GCC 4.4+ wrt #277561.

