  Fix HOMEPAGE and SRC_URI wrt #266702.

  17 Dec 2008; Peter Alfredsen <loki_val@gentoo.org>
  +files/fireflies-2.07-gcc43.patch, fireflies-2.07.ebuild:
  Fix bug 228219. Thanks to Jabari R. Roberts for the patch.

